headline: 3 Stocks Poised for Growth as Trump Doubles Steel Tariffs
summary: Trump's tariff hike to 50% on steel imports could ignite gains for NUE, STLD and CLF as demand shifts to U.S. producers.

headline: Cleveland-Cliffs (CLF) Surges 5.3%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Cleveland-Cliffs (CLF) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might not help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
